<h2 id="setting-up-the-javascript">Setting up the JavaScript <a class="headerlink" href="date-picker-field#setting-up-the-javascript" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Next, in our template, add the <code>jQuery(document.ready)</code> block. Hook it up with
<code>$('.js-datepicker').datepicker()</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="9e05fe1381">
